name: Obi-Wan Kenobi, Jedi Knight (V)
Lore: 'Padawan learner promoted to Jedi Knight after his encounter with Darth Maul. Has sworn to train Anakin Skywalker, even if the Jedi Council forbids it.',
Text: 'Deploys -1 to [Episode I] sites. During a battle (or duel) with a Dark Jedi, unless Obi-Wan''s Journal on table, may lose 1 Force to cancel a just drawn duel or weapon destiny. Immune to attrition < 5.',
